data.description: 4 BR, 3 FBA home on beautiful tree lined lot with 2 car garage and carport. This home is set in Caseys Manor Community which is close to shopping and entertainment.   Neutral colors through out. 3 BR on upper level with 1 FBA, 1 BR on lower level with 1 FBA. Great Room and updated kitchen on main level and 1 FBA. Mature tree's in front yard... Large front porch across front of home to  gather for conversation, coffee or reading. Nice size patio in back yard with so much room for family gatherings/cookouts. Beautiful family home in every sense of the word!
